      "content": "rest doesn't fix the fact that i'm drowning. it just gives me more time to think about how impossible this is. i feel like i'm just a burden to everyone because of this, and honestly, i just want the noise to stop. i want a way to just... not have to deal with this anymore. like, is there even a version of life where this doesn't consume everything? because it feels like this is just how it ends.",
